spec_data.Name: nodejs-util-deprecate
spec_data.Description:
In Node.js, this module simply re-exports the util.deprecate() function.
In the web browser (i.e. via browserify), a browser-specific implementation
of the util.deprecate() function is used.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 04:21:15 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: The Node.js `util.deprecate()` function with browser support
